{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775851272059,"sessionID":"ses_287044941ffeDRIXC5QvJ9yjn1","part":{"id":"prt_d78fbf32b001C2E9QECozyWppb","messageID":"msg_d78fbe536001Adsqxlb4bUL3LO","sessionID":"ses_287044941ffeDRIXC5QvJ9yjn1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_b9532d634d8c48baa88c5e09","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Redis storage in `pkg/store`.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-013\n10: - **Module**: `pkg/store`\n11: - **Language**: Go\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Base Specs**: \n14:   - TBD\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ## Background\n19: \n20: TBD\n21: \n22: ---\n23: \n24: ## Acceptance Criteria\n25: \n26: - [ ] TBD\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## References\n31: \n32: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md`\n\n(End of file - total 32 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Redis storage in `pkg/store`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-013\n- **Module**: `pkg/store`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Specs**: \n  - TBD\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\nTBD","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775851272041,"end":1775851272057}}}}
